    "causal_summary": "Phase 018 removed legacy packet `memory/` saves as the main continuity surface, but the graph and retrieval stack still depends on packet-level metadata for relationships, ranking, and key-file recovery. This packet formalizes the replacement contract from [research.md](./research.md): one `graph-metadata.json` per spec-folder root, split into merge-safe `manual` fields and fully regenerated `derived` fields, refreshed on canonical save, and indexed as `document_type='graph_metadata'`.",
